text.author: Melissa Lucy
text.title: college day in my life: preparing for finals, study guides, yoga, etc
text.summary: An FGCU student tells about how she is studying for her final exam by going over chapters covering the male and female reproductive systems, urinary system and fluid balance, and then goes to exchange a pair of Vans shoes at a DSW shoe store.
